.alert.alert-info.mb-0
  %h5.fw-semibold.mb-2 Ultimate goal
  %p.mb-3
    Confirm every ability change in this batch, certify the awards, and save once—after you are sure the selected levels match what this teammate has demonstrated.

  %h6.fw-semibold.mb-2 What each section means
  %ul.mb-3
    %li
      %strong Certification
      — your attestation applies to every
      %em new
      milestone in this batch; the stored note is fixed as
      %code= 'Bulk Milestone Adjustment'
      \.
    %li
      %strong Milestones being removed
      — levels that will be cleared or lowered; removing milestones can delete related observable moments when no observation exists yet.
    %li
      %strong Summary by ability
      — before/after levels;
      %strong Company-visible new
      shows only the highest new level per ability that teammates will see (lower new levels in the same ability stay private).

  %p.mb-0
    %strong Before saving:
    use
    %em= 'Back to edit'
    if any row needs a different level. Saving cannot be undone—double-check uncertain abilities on the edit step first.
